  "description": "A spacious and functional two-chamber inverter refrigerator from the LG family. The device is based on an inverter compressor, which, above all, is distinguished by increased reliability, as well as a higher level of energy efficiency (corresponds to class A ++) and a lower level of generated noise (does not exceed 36 dB). The working chambers have their own cooling circuits, which provides for the possibility of fully independent adjustment of their work. Refrigerator LG GB-P31DSLZN is not deprived of spacious interior space. The total volume of working chambers is 341 liters with a fairly standard body height of 203 cm. DoorCooling + technology provides the possibility of uniform and fast cooling of all shelves and baskets, including door ones. The 234 l refrigerator compartment boasts a special freshness zone. The 107 l freezer has three food drawers, is able to maintain a temperature of -24 ° C, and also freeze up to 12 kg of fresh food per day. There is an automatic defrosting system No Frost, which takes care of both the refrigerator compartment and the freezer zone. Touch type control panel, but located inside the refrigerator compartment. The model does not consume more than 254 kWh per year.",
